          "substrate": "Optional - coco coir, paper towel, or sphagnum moss if desired",
          "diet": "Flying insects preferred throughout life. L1-L3: fruit flies (6-16 twice weekly), L4-L6: 4 flies 3x weekly, Adults: 6 flies 3x weekly (double for mated females). Blue bottle flies ideal for adults",
