          "Females can lay up to 8 oothecae after mating, with each ooth containing up to 50-60 nymphs"
        ],
        "buying_tips": "Look for healthy, active nymphs between L3-L5 for best success. Ensure you have appropriately sized flying feeders (fruit flies for young, blue bottles for older) before purchasing. Be prepared to upgrade enclosure size multiple times as they grow \u2014 adults need substantial space that many beginners underestimate.",
