          "substrate": "1-2 inches of coconut fiber, peat moss, or paper towels; bioactive setups work well",
          "diet": "L1-L2 nymphs: melanogaster fruit flies. L3-L4: hydei fruit flies (2-3 every other day). L5-adult: house flies, blue bottle flies (3-4 every 2-3 days). Adults prefer flying prey. Never feed crickets - they carry harmful bacteria",
