          "diet": "Slings: fruit flies or pinhead crickets every 4-5 days. Juveniles: appropriately sized crickets weekly. Adults: large crickets, roaches, or locusts every 10-14 days",
          "water": "Shallow water dish always available. Light misting once weekly if needed. Keep substrate slightly moist at bottom, dry on top",
          "lifespan": "Females: 10-15 years. Males: 3-5 years",
