        "buying_tips": "Look for captive-bred specimens only - wild-caught are more defensive and stressed. Start with a well-established juvenile (2-3 inches) rather than tiny slings or defensive adults. Ensure the seller provides a secure, escape-proof container as these are master escape artists.",
        "faqs": [
          {
